cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.SE 

The paper discusses security issues in Ad Hoc Routing Protocols in Mobile Ad hoc Networks (MANETs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses security threats and attacks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also mentions performance analysis, which could place it in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper discusses solutions to mitigate security vulnerabilities, which could place it in cs.SE (Software Engineering).
